criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient over 18 years of age ;

          -  Have followed the training to the accompaniment proposed by the research team of
             SPICES ;

          -  Have signed the accompanying person's ethics charter co-created by the champions'
             research team.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Refusal of a champion to participate in the qualitative study ;

          -  Patients under judicial protection (guardianship, curatorship, ...).
